# =============================================================================
# RENOZ Energy Website - Environment Variables Template
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values
# Never commit .env to version control!

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Supabase Configuration
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Get these from your Supabase project settings: https://app.supabase.com
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# Service Role Key (ONLY for admin operations - keep secret!)
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_supabase_service_role_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cloudflare Turnstile (Spam Protection)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Sign up at: https://dash.cloudflare.com/sign-up/turnstile
# Free tier: Unlimited requests
VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=your_turnstile_site_key_here
TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY=your_turnstile_secret_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Google Maps (Optional - for Address Autocomplete)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Get key from: https://console.cloud.google.com/google/maps-apis
# Enable "Places API" and "Maps JavaScript API"
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Resend Email Service
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Sign up at: https://resend.com
# Free tier: 100 emails/day, 3,000 emails/month
RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_resend_api_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Google Analytics 4 (Optional)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Get your Measurement ID from: https://analytics.google.com
# Create GA4 property and copy the G-XXXXXXXXXX ID
VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=your_ga4_measurement_id_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Email Configuration (Optional - defaults provided)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Contact Form Emails
CONTACT_FORM_TO_EMAIL=sales@renoz.energy
CONTACT_FORM_FROM_EMAIL=RENOZ Energy <noreply@renoz.energy>

# Warranty Registration Emails
WARRANTY_TO_EMAIL=support@renoz.energy
WARRANTY_FROM_EMAIL=RENOZ Energy <noreply@renoz.energy>

# =============================================================================
# Setup Instructions
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. SUPABASE SETUP
#    - Create account at https://supabase.com
#    - Create new project
#    - Go to Settings > API to get:
#      * Project URL (VITE_SUPABASE_URL)
#      * Anon/Public Key (VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY)
#    - Run the SQL in supabase-schema.sql to create tables
#    - Create 'warranty-uploads' storage bucket (see setup-storage.sql)
#    - Service Role Key only needed for admin operations (uncomment if required)
#
# 2. TURNSTILE SETUP
#    - Go to https://dash.cloudflare.com/sign-up/turnstile
#    - Add a new site (use your domain or 'localhost' for dev)
#    - Copy Site Key (VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY)
#    - Copy Secret Key (TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY)
#
# 3. RESEND SETUP
#    - Sign up at https://resend.com
#    - Verify your domain (or use resend.dev for testing)
#    - Go to API Keys and create a new key
#    - Copy the API key (starts with 're_')
#
# 4. ANALYTICS (Optional but Recommended)
#    - Plausible Analytics is pre-integrated (privacy-focused, no cookies)
#    - Just add your domain in Plausible dashboard: plausible.io
#    - Google Analytics 4 (optional, more comprehensive tracking)
#      * Sign up at: https://analytics.google.com
#      * Create GA4 property and get Measurement ID (G-XXXXXXXXXX)
#      * Copy to VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID
#    - Vercel Analytics is automatic (no setup needed)
#    - Web Vitals tracking is automatic
#
# 5. DEPLOYMENT (Vercel/Netlify)
#    - Add all environment variables to your deployment platform
#    - Make sure to add both VITE_ prefixed and non-prefixed vars
#    - VITE_ vars are exposed to the client (safe for public)
#    - Non-VITE_ vars are server-only (keep secret!)
#    - See DEPLOYMENT.md for full deployment guide
#
# =============================================================================

